              11:24 27/09/99: Page 3 (HHH) COURTS Pinochet Lead
  ------------------------------------------------------------------------
The allegations of torture include claims that one woman was beaten and threats
made to rape her sister.<
Several cases involved victims being suspended, beaten and electrocuted.<
One man was forced to take hallucinogenic drugs it is alleged and another man
was locked into a small cage and suffered electric shocks.<
In another alleged case a woman suffered interrogations while she was naked
and while threats were made to attack her nine-year-old daughter.<
Other victims, including several women were deprived of sleep, food and water.
Victims were also threatened with death or disfigurement.<
